tat may be necessary.', 'Metabolism', 'Caution is advised when osilodrostat is coadministered with CYP450 3A4 inhibitors.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/290711/', '', '', '', 1767369485);
